  <description><![CDATA[<p>This 9-night tour is an excellent overview to Switzerland's special highlights, designed for those seeking a true taste of this stunning country. Visiting many resorts on a self guided base, including unforgettable experiences on two of the most spectacular panoramic journeys in the world, the ‘Bernina’ and ‘Glacier Express’.  Featuring the beautiful lakeside setting of <a data-udi="umb://document/70b1a325037e4112bc5e6feeb41d725f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/70b1a325037e4112bc5e6feeb41d725f}" title="Lake Lucerne">Lake Lucerne</a> with its pedestrianised Old Town and nearby Mount Pilatus. Experience the world-famous St. Moritz and ride onboard the Glacier Express to the ‘Matterhorn village’ of <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a>, and then the option to continue on to the dramatic scenery of Grindelwald in the <a data-udi="umb://document/d1bb27ef1cf04b448d45b9dcbfeb2771" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d1bb27ef1cf04b448d45b9dcbfeb2771}" title="Bernese Oberland">Bernese Oberland</a>.</p>
<p>Amongst the highlights are a day excursion on the spectacular ‘Bernina Express’ train from St. Moritz to Tirano near the Italian border, and the rail journey from St.Moritz to <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a> on the ‘Glacier Express’ where we have arranged for you to enjoy lunch on board. Each of your transfers is by 1st class rail, so all you need to do is sit back and admire the scenery. With a half-fare travel card for reductions on Switzerland’s superb transport network and excursions also included, you have plenty of opportunities to explore, cruise, hike, or simply relax during free time in four of Switzerland’s contrasting ‘Cantons.</p>
<p> </p>
